0b debugreg data7            | Abstract Data 7
0c debugreg data8            | Abstract Data 8
0d debugreg data9            | Abstract Data 9
0e debugreg data10           | Abstract Data 10
0f debugreg data11           | Abstract Data 11
10 debugreg dmcontrol        | Debug Module Control
11 debugreg dmstatus         | Debug Module Status
12 debugreg hartinfo         | Hart Info
13 debugreg haltsum1         | Halt Summary 1
14 debugreg hawindowsel      | Hart Array Window Select
15 debugreg hawindow         | Hart Array Window
16 debugreg abstractcs       | Abstract Control and Status
17 debugreg command          | Abstract Command
18 debugreg abstractauto     | Abstract Command Autoexec
19 debugreg confstrptr0      | Configuration String Pointer 0
1a debugreg confstrptr1      | Configuration String Pointer 1
1b debugreg confstrptr2      | Configuration String Pointer 2
1c debugreg confstrptr3      | Configuration String Pointer 3
1d debugreg nextdm           | Next Debug Module
20 debugreg progbuf0         | Program Buffer 0
21 debugreg progbuf1         | Program Buffer 1
